    "description": "踏上探矿者的坚固靴子，进入神秘莫测且被邪恶诅咒困扰的科尔德里奇荒野。你的任务是：发现珍贵资源，解决复杂谜题，战略性地管理合同以最大化收益。在这段迷人的冒险中，揭开行会的神秘秘密及其对科尔德里奇的控制。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >探索未驯服的荒野</h2>穿越科尔德里奇未探知领地，为强大的行会绘制资源地图。每一步进入荒野都带来新的挑战和机遇，面对危险的地形不断前行。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052500/extras/42e1e4e4a10c4b23043d99e362f101ab.poster.avif?t=1769676114\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052500/extras/42e1e4e4a10c4b23043d99e362f101ab.webm?t=1769676114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052500/extras/42e1e4e4a10c4b23043d99e362f101ab.mp4?t=1769676114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >高风险，高回报</h2>通过选择正确的合同来精心计划你的探险。你会采取计算好的风险，还是敢于冒险以获取更大的回报？你的决定可能带来财富或危险。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052500/extras/a68903ccfac983e177a1088b25c421a7.poster.avif?t=1769676114\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052500/extras/a68903ccfac983e177a1088b25c421a7.webm?t=1769676114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052500/extras/a68903ccfac983e177a1088b25c421a7.mp4?t=1769676114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >掌握行动规划</h2>通过精心规划你的行动来完成合同。利用地形和装备获取优势，避开障碍，效率完成目标。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052500/extras/c083382c16582173e78b3bd302c24148.poster.avif?t=1769676114\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052500/extras/c083382c16582173e78b3bd302c24148.webm?t=1769676114\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052500/extras/c083382c16582173e78b3bd302c24148.mp4?t=1769676114\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >解锁新角色</h2>体验rogue-lite风格的进展，解锁新角色和物品。每次游戏都带来新的挑战和机会。看看你能坚持多久，能多深揭开科尔德里奇的秘密。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052500/extras/c412865ee111ca2dcfa8019c3b9772e4.avif?t=1769676114\" width=616 height=300 /></span><br><br>踏上这段激动人心的冒险，每一个决定都至关重要，荒野既藏有宝藏也有秘密。你会接受挑战并揭开行会的秘密吗？科尔德里奇的荒野等待着你的专业知识",
